  "original_title": "Quickee.lk donates digital teaching system to S. Thomas\u2019 College, Mt Lavinia",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Quickee.lk donates digital teaching system to S. Thomas\u2019 College, Mt Lavinia",
      "author": "Thilina Walpola",
      "body_lines": [
        "Quickee.lk, Sri Lanka\u2019s favourite online marketplace, recently provided a state-of-the-art digital interactive smartboard system to S. Thomas\u2019 College, Mt Lavinia. This provision is one of the many social empowerment projects conducted by Quickee.lk and it aims to facilitate students with an enhanced learning experience.",
        "Mr. Sammy Akbar, CEO of Quickee.lk said: \u201cWe are indeed happy to equip our students with latest technology to continue their studies in an advanced manner. This is a highly versatile smartboard that incorporates all the necessary features to improve the quality of learning and ensure high level of interaction during learning. We believe that the students at S. Thomas\u2019 College will be largely benefitted through this, and we expect to further strengthen our efforts towards advancing the local education system.\u201d",
        "The smartboard, with its large, 75-inch display panel, is a modern powerhouse in delivering interactive teaching and learning. It can instantly store various drawings, and notes in its 1 TB hard disk drive for later retrieval and the dual operating system enables the 75E29P3 smartboard to perform in many demanding teaching scenarios that students of S. Thomas\u2019 often require.",
        "The smartboard\u2019s multi-tasking capabilities help students to conveniently engage in group activities and presentations. Both the teachers and students can store their assignments, lessons, and other data, so that all the learning materials can be accessed from one place. This smartboard can also be used to watch educational videos and listen to podcasts and audios, which help students to expand their knowledge. Since it supports faster USB connectivity, playing high quality videos too is a possibility on this device. Being a lightweight device, it can be easily shifted from one class to another and can be placed in a moving stand or set up in a wall mount.",
        "Quickee.lk, since its inception, has extended its support to schools with a special focus on enhancing the quality of education through many contributions. It not only empowers students by providing a better education, but also continues to uplift sports in schools. Among its notable efforts, Quickee.lk, recently stepped forward to empower Sri Lanka schools\u2019 rugby 2022 and is looking forward to driving more school outreach initiatives.",
        "Increasing productivity and reducing costs with HR Pro SaaS cloud technology",
        "Leave a Reply Cancel replyYour email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *Comment Name *",
        "Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment."
